name: RoseWater
description: Rosewater is one of the most soothing drinks in the world. You do not need to be photographed it by the person who drinks it to show. It can be displayed in an old apothecary, which gives it a certain originality and nostalgia, and at the same time has the same sense of calm. For this purpose, I created an apothecary simulation inside my photography studio and took a photo of it.
